      "writtenOn": "2020-10-06T22:55:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Session should not reset on stop. It should instead pause, leaving the cursor (current_record_iterator_) wherever it is when stop is called. If the user wants to reset the current session to the beginning, they should call SeekToTime(0). This library should not presume to do it for them.",
